%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make sad, to sadden"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cause to mourn or lament"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to grieve","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to grieve, to mourn, to lament"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become sorrowful, sad, or unhappy","examples":[{"text":"لَا تَحْزَنْ إِنَّ اللهَ مَعَنَا","english":"Do not grieve; indeed God is with us."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become rough"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be or become rugged and hard"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَزَنَ (ḥazana) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sadness, grief, sorrow","examples":[{"text":"رَأَيْتُ الدَّهْرَ مُخْتَلِفًا يَدُورُ -- فَلَا حُزْنٌ يَدُومُ وَلَا سُرُورُ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"rugged and hard ground","examples":[{"text":"Hadith\nاللَّهُمَّ لَا سَهْلَ إِلَّا مَا جَعَلْتَهُ سَهْلًا وَأَنْتَ تَجْعَلُ ٱلْحَزْنَ إِنْ شِئْتَ سَهْلًا\nal-lahumma lā sahla ʔillā mā jaʕaltahu sahlan waʔanta tajʕalu l-ḥazna ʔin šiʔta sahlan","english":"(please add an English translation of this quotation)"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَزِنَ (ḥazina) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sadness, grief"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"sad, sorrowful, grieved"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7893","headword_ar":"حَزِنَ","root":"Hzn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HazanN","text_ar":"حَزَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHtzn","text_ar":"احتزن","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHz~n","text_ar":"تحزّن","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHAzn","text_ar":"تحازن","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he grieved, mourned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lamented;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was sorrowful, sad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unhappy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for him"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, Msb, K.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taHozano","text_ar":"لَا تَحْزَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taHozanuwA","text_ar":"لَا تَحْزَنُوا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [ix. 40, &c., and iii. 133], do not denote a prohibition of getting"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"does not come by the will of man: the real meaning is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do not thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ye, that which engenders"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"do not thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ye, acquire"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Er-Rághib. [But this requires consideration; or, rather, is not in every case admissible.])       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hazanahu","text_ar":"حَزَنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzonN","text_ar":"حُزْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHznhu","text_ar":"احزنهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(another person, S,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an affair, or an event, or a case, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused him to be affected with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which see below; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grieved him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused him to mourn"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lament,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be sorrowful"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sad"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unhappy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]: (S, Msb, K:) accord. to Yz, (S,) the former is of the dial. of Kureysh; and the latter, of the dial. of Temeem: (S, Msb:) and so say Th and Az: (Msb, TA:) but the former is said to be the more approved: (TA:) or, accord. to AZ, the aor. of the former is used, but not the pret.; (Msb, TA;) and when the act is ascribed to God, the latter verb is used: Z, also, says that what is well known in usage is the employing the pret. of the latter and the aor. of the former: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHznhu","text_ar":"احزنهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made him"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haziyn","text_ar":"حَزِين"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hazanahu","text_ar":"حَزَنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [in some copies of the K ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hz~nhu","text_ar":"حزّنهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be in him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hazanahu","text_ar":"حَزَنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it caused him to fall into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huzon","text_ar":"حُزْن"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hazunati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"حَزُنَتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuzuwnapN","text_ar":"حُزُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstHznt","text_ar":"استحزنت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ground was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, rough,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rugged and hard."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-  One says also of a beast that is not easy to ride upon,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaHozunu Alma$oYa","text_ar":"يَحْزُنُ المَشْىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is rough in pace"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi HuzuwnapN","text_ar":"فِيهِ حُزُونَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In him is roughness"},{"kind":"text","text":"in pace]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA","Sb"]}]}}